  "body": "### Description\r\nWhen we add a new maintained peer via the REST API `admin_addPeer` endpoint, rather than directly adding the peer to our discovery peer table, we should attempt to bond with the peer.  This means that we'll only publish to the discovery DHT if it is live and responds to our bonding attempt.\r\n\r\nSee comment here: https://github.com/hyperledger/besu/pull/1177#discussion_r466048508\r\n",
